<div><strong>Project Tasks</strong>
Project tasks are items that appears under a project as action items. to customize the list of project tasks please do the following.
<ol>
<li> Click on Settings
<li> Click on Tasks Manager
<li> Add Tasks that should appear on a project
<li> Press Save
<li> Repeat the process to add more tasks. 
</ol>
</div>

<div><strong>Project Parameters</strong>
Project Paramters are input items that you track per project, in order to customize the list of project paramters 
<ol>
<li> Click on Settings
<li> Click on Project Params
<li> Type the Param Name (this should not have any spaces)
<li> Select if the Paramter input should be in type of a text box, radio or checkbox
<li> For textbox enter the size of the field
<li> Enter the description that should appear before the text box
<li> Press Save
<li> Repeat the process to enter as many paramters that you would like to track.
</ol>
